  "description": "A nighttime view of a city skyline and bridge, illuminated by a vibrant fireworks display. The fireworks burst in various colors \u2013 reds, greens, and whites \u2013 against the dark sky. Below, a long bridge stretches across dark water, its lights reflecting on the surface. In the background, a city skyline featuring numerous illuminated buildings is visible, with some buildings standing out with distinct architectural designs, notably a series of lit-up towers. The overall scene conveys a sense of celebration and urban beauty.",
